          class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted leading-relaxed"
        >
          <p>
            Most scheduling tools - including Google Calendar and major SaaS
            platforms - force users to manually select their timezone from
            dropdown menus. This creates friction, confusion, and mistakes.
            Users forget to select their timezone, pick the wrong one from long
            lists, or don't understand which timezone they should choose.
            CalendHub solves this completely with automatic timezone detection
            that requires zero user interaction.
          </p>

