            Our system automatically detects where you are the moment you visit
            a booking page. No dropdowns appear. No settings to configure. The
            booking page immediately shows available times in your local
            timezone. If you're in California, you see Pacific times. If you're
            in London, you see GMT times. If you're in Tokyo, you see JST times.
            The system handles all timezone conversions automatically in the
            background.
          </p>

