            flow. Booking confirmations show times in the booker's timezone.
            Calendar invites include proper timezone data so appointments appear
            correctly regardless of where attendees travel. Email reminders
            reference local times. Every interaction displays
            timezone-appropriate information without users needing to think
            about it. This seamless experience makes global scheduling as simple
            as local scheduling.
          </p>
